column16: Aaron Altherr flies out to left fielder Derek Dietrich.
Freddy Galvis grounds out, second baseman Dee Gordon to first baseman Justin Bour.   Darnell Sweeney to 3rd.
Darnell Sweeney doubles (4) on a line drive to right fielder Cole Gillespie.   Odubel Herrera scores.
Cameron Rupp flies out to center fielder Marcell Ozuna.   Odubel Herrera to 3rd.
Odubel Herrera doubles (30) on a line drive to right fielder Cole Gillespie.
